# Contributing to soroban-shield-contracts

Thank you for contributing to Soroban Shield. Please read the org-wide
[CONTRIBUTING.md](https://github.com/Soroban-shield/soroban-shield/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md)
for workflow details.

## Development

```bash
cargo test --features testutils
cargo fmt --all
cargo clippy -- -D warnings
```

## Module guidelines

- Keep modules self-contained under `src/contracts/<name>/`
- Add unit tests in-module and integration tests under `tests/`
- Document public functions with security rationale
